ttering spectral profiles\nfor air under sub-atmospheric conditions can be generated via the Tenti-S6\nmodel, for given gas-phase and detection conditions ($p$, $T$, $\\lambda_i$, and\n$\\theta$), and for values for the gas transport coefficients.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Dec 2020 16:43:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-12-17"}
