 for\nfuture Stage IV surveys and we propose to include the uncertainty on the AGN\nfeedback amplitude by marginalizing over this parameter using multiple\nsimulations such as those presented in this paper. Finally, we explore the\npossibility of mitigating the impact of baryons by filtering the $M_{\\rm ap}$\nmap but find that this process would require to suppress the small-scale\ninformation to a point where the constraints would no longer be competitive.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 Dec 2020 14:21:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 Feb 2021 17:44:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-28"}
